data.title: 4 Institute Deputy Director Kwezi Tabaro Receives Prestigious Hubert Humphrey Fellowship
5Institute Deputy Director Kwezi Tabaro Receives Prestigious Hubert Humphrey Fellowship
data.author: Akello Jane

featured_image.alt: Our long-time deputy director Kwezi Tabaro is the recipient of the prestigious Hubert Humphrey Fellowship 2024, marking a significant recognition of his outstanding contribution to shaping leadership development programmes at the LéO Africa Institute.
